      // escape bugs are impossible by construction. Editing is grid-native:
      // insert-push on type, pull on delete, free arrows; Enter inserts a row and
      // cascades the rows below down, ABSORBING into the first empty row, else
      // growing the region (§reflow; the inter-region push is slice B).
